text-gray-400 transition-colors hover:text-white" href="/contact">Contact</a></div></div><main class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-12 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><article class="legal-article"><h1>Contact Us</h1><p>We’re a small team and we read every email. Please use the address that best fits your inquiry — it helps us route messages quickly.</p><div class="not-prose mt-8 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2"><a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection#077472777768757347636866656b62296a62" class="group block rounded-xl border border-gray-800/70 bg-gray-900/30 p-5 transition-colors hover:border-brand-500/50 hover:bg-gray-900/60"><div class="mb-3 inline-flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-brand-500/10 text-brand-300"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-message-square h-4 w-4"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"></path></svg></div><h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-white">General &amp; support</h3><p class="mt-1 font-mono text-sm text-brand-400 group-hover:underline"><span class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="e99a9c9999869b9da98d86888b858cc7848c">[email&#160;protected]</span></p><p class="mt-2 text-xs leading-relaxed text-gray-400">Questions about the Service, billing, or your account.</p></a><a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection#84f7e1e7f1f6edf0fdc4e0ebe5e6e8e1aae9e1" class="group block rounded-xl border border-gray-800/70 bg-gray-900/30 p-5 transition-colors hover:border-brand-500/50 hover:bg-gray-900/60"><div class="mb-3 inline-flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-brand-500/10 text-brand-300"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-shield h-4 w-4"><path d="M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.0